# Runtime npm dependencies for the catalog loader (Phase catalog.A, v1.5.0).
# Negations whitelist ajv + ajv-formats and their transitive runtime deps so
# the packaged VSIX can `require()` them at extension activation. Without
# these, `node_modules/**` above would strip every dependency from the bundle.
!node_modules/ajv/**
!node_modules/ajv-formats/**
!node_modules/fast-deep-equal/**
!node_modules/fast-uri/**
!node_modules/json-schema-traverse/**
!node_modules/require-from-string/**
